description: A pun involving a duck and a cement mixer
title: Quacky Pavement
n_1: A duck and its friend are talking near a cement mixer.
c1_1: Hey, want to hear a joke?
n_2: The duck looks at the friend with a playful expression.
c1_2: What do you get if you put a duck in a cement mixer?
n_3: The friend looks curious and intrigued.
n_4: Both share a moment of laughter.
